Class UndirectedWeightedListGraph

java.lang.Object
  edu.stanford.math.plex4.graph.UndirectedWeightedListGraph
All Implemented Interfaces:
AbstractUndirectedGraph, AbstractWeightedUndirectedGraph, java.lang.Iterable<edu.stanford.math.primitivelib.autogen.pair.IntIntPair>
public class UndirectedWeightedListGraph
extends java.lang.Object
implements AbstractWeightedUndirectedGraph

This class implements the functionality of an undirected weighted graph. It uses an adjacency list representation. See the class UndirectedListGraph for more information about the internal representation.

Author:
Andrew Tausz
